import { Image, Text, View } from "react-native"
import tw from "twrnc"

export default () => {
    return( 
    <View style = {tw`flex flex-row m-0 h-full w-full`}>
        <View style = {tw`h-full w-1/2 p-20`}>
            <View style = {tw`flex flex-col h-5/6 rounded-lg`}>
                <Text style = {tw`font-medium text-3xl text-center`}>
                    WELCOME   BACK
                </Text>
                <Text style = {tw`text-gray-300`}>
                    Welcome back! Please enter your details. 
                </Text>
                <View style = {tw`py-10 `}>
                    <Text>
                        Email
                    </Text>
                </View>
            </View>    
        </View>
        <View style = {tw`h-full w-1/2 bg-gray-200`}>
            <Image />        
        </View>
    </View>
)}
